{"tid":1650519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔獸世界》前首席設計師加入抵制暴雪：我現在已畫下了底線！","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:20:52.000Z","uid":260367,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d778a6341cc3456a93d2a66eabfb0e9c577009","tid":1650519,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"事件一出引起軒然大波，不少網民都相繼表態要杯葛暴雪，「魔獸世界」的前首席設計師兼有份參與開發「暗黑破壞神2」、「星海爭霸」等遊戲的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Mark Kern</strong></span></span>也都在其推特上表態加入杯葛行列，並已刪除暴雪的遊戲啟動器，他表示除非暴雪收回對Blitzchung的處理，否則將不再玩「魔獸世界」，並呼籲眾人響應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4HgxyA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4HgxyA.png&h=3f2fbf9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家幫幫手，去佢 Twtter 幫手 RT / Like : </span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Grummz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGrummz&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGVMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=435c5ef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Grummz</a>"},{"pid":"36bf101f5f391f852d7a8cb88628f8c4c1e1fbc5","tid":1650519,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnAJUrV.jpg&h=222a48c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f948860f94e58c15b4026145adec724b2a3ce5a6","tid":1650519,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"451b5d13c84610418e0496742c6d1288588d29cf","tid":1650519,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"留言，晚上返黎推"},{"pid":"fec49ced106661706fddbc80c5333c3e727a607f","tid":1650519,"uid":172454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191013/large/1570898058_a833.gif\" /><br />\n【本報訊】為響應全球抵制遊戲商暴雪，暴雪旗下遊戲《魔獸世界》（WoW）的香港公會HK Essence，日前亦決定暫停所有公會活動，並呼籲會員抵制暴雪，直至撤回對Blitzchung的懲罰和作出適當回應。管理員星仔解釋，暴雪出品的遊戲陪伴他成長，但暴雪現已不是「玩家優先」的公司，只為迎合中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n玩家嘆暴雪為人幣變質<br />\n台灣伺服器公會HK Essence成立於2013年。星仔表示，當時出團做任務多講普通話，但鑑於有不少香港玩家，於是成立香港公會，同聲同氣玩得更過癮。公會累積約1,500名會員，現時每晚逾百人在線，多數會員支持抵制行動，不少人刪game、刪賬號罷玩。<br />\n<br />\n星仔指，魔獸世界及其前身《魔獸爭霸3》陪伴不少港人成長。他指初中時家中開始有電腦或有零用錢去網吧，每日放學和朋友玩數小時《魔獸爭霸3》，到大學就沉迷《魔獸世界》，「當時好震撼，有世界觀咁宏大嘅遊戲」。透過在遊戲內搞公會活動，更將虛擬世界帶到現實世界，「玩家之間會出嚟食飯，亦有情侶因為呢個公會先相識」。<br />\n<br />\n「以前坊間都話『暴雪出品、必屬佳品』」，但他批評暴雪日漸失去「玩家優先」精神，不再以遊戲質素取勝，只為迎合中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n星仔舉例指，去年暴雪和中國網易合作的經典遊戲《Diablo》手機版，就因為與玩家期望有巨大落差而劣評如潮。<br />\n<br />\n星仔續指，Blitzchung一事更凸顯暴雪不尊重對人權和自由的表態，即使昨日讓步亦絕不收貨，「佢不斷合理化自己嘅做法，唔係認錯」，希望暴雪真誠道歉，並在「生意和核心價值之間揀返核心價值」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191013/20786155?fbclid=IwAR3YuVWJQSrEzMpA32WJ8MFENegBcBhmm0WMNvc5cwW0zmb8FycpUDyW5XM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191013%2F20786155%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3YuVWJQSrEzMpA32WJ8MFENegBcBhmm0WMNvc5cwW0zmb8FycpUDyW5XM&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGVMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=1cf868b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191013%2F20786155%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3YuVWJQSrEzMpA32WJ8MFENegBcBhmm0WMNvc5cwW0zmb8FycpUDyW5XM&h=2a9497c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191013/20786155?fbclid=IwAR3YuVWJQSrEzMpA32WJ8MFENegBcBhmm0WMNvc5cwW0zmb8FycpUDyW5XM</a>"},{"pid":"2358c8afbfdaa9415b0b009f8b403e296f6bde0b","tid":1650519,"uid":278431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"73ec26f7f278ca848c41fc203993b8dd2ee7d17d","tid":1650519,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}